i der eigenen Arbeit am Grundriss anregen zu lassen. Die einleitenden theoretischen und historischen Essays sind neu verfasst beziehungsweise aktualisiert worden und bieten ein übersichtlich strukturiertes Bild der Wohnungsbautypologie und ihrer Entwicklung.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aArchitecture, DomesticvDesigns and plans. 4aErschließung. 4aGrundriss. 4aGrundrissorganisation. 4aWohnanlage. 4aWohnungsbau. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aHeckmann, Oliver, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeckmann, Oliver, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchneider, Friederike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchneider, Friederike, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aZapel, Eric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2017z9783110547719oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303561141040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303560969140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035609691423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035609691/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017